Konolfingen       20:52 20:52
Langnau i.E       21:05 21:06
Trubschachen      21:12 21:14
Escholzmatt		  21:21 21:21
Schüpfheim        21:28 21:29
Entlebuch		  21:35	21:35
Wolhusen          21:44
VM Nr. 4487
Wolhusen		         21:45
Malters		      21:52  21:52
Luzern			  22:03       
-->
